OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some sunshine. Then
OL,7,Fthe rest of the night will be mainly
OL,8,Fdry with variable amounts of cloud. A
OL,9,Ffew showers across Western Tayside
OL,10,Flater.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FMainly cloudy with some
OL,13,Fshowery rain, but drier with some
OL,14,Fbrightness across towards the east
OL,15,Fcoast.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:
OL,18,FOutbreaks of rain will spread east on
OL,19,FSaturday, occasionally heavy later.
OL,20,FScattered showers on Sunday. Further
OL,21,Frain likely on Monday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
